1
00:01:44,250 --> 00:01:48,720
[A LOVER IN THE MORTAL WORLD]

2
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,840
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,200
Miss Ling?

4
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:04,610
How did you get in here?

5
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:05,790
And who

6
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:07,090
let you in?

7
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,550
I snuck in by myself.

8
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,710
So now, just anyone can walk

9
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:16,370
into my Tianlang Pass prison?

10
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:17,740
It seems Huang Jian

11
00:02:17,770 --> 00:02:19,430
doesn't want his job anymore.

12
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,790
No, no, no.

13
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,700
I'm actually here to see Zhao Gao.

14
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,120
This prison is heavily guarded.

15
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,150
I couldn't have gotten in at all.

16
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:31,050
But I saved Huang Jian's son before.

17
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:32,450
And I begged him so hard.

18
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,120
He softened up...

19
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,680
and let me in.

20
00:02:36,950 --> 00:02:39,010
Then why are you looking for Zhao Gao?

21
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,030
I...

22
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:41,990
Do you still want to marry him?

23
00:02:41,990 --> 00:02:43,110
How could I?

24
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,940
Then why are you looking for him?

25
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:49,190
Not going to tell me, huh?

26
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,430
I'll go ask Zhao Gao.

27
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,890
He'll definitely tell me.

28
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,280
You—

29
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,000
General Xiao.

30
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:00,960
Zhao Gao.

31
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,680
You two...

32
00:03:11,610 --> 00:03:12,450
Xiao Chi,

33
00:03:12,550 --> 00:03:14,440
when are you going to let me out?

34
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,240
I came here

35
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,870
just to tell you about this.

36
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:17,870
In half a month,

37
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,579
you will be taken back to the capital.

38
00:03:19,579 --> 00:03:21,150
Then I will report to His Majesty

39
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:22,190
about how you

40
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,360
withheld military pay

41
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,150
and forced Changmo women to marry you.

42
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:25,680
Right.

43
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:26,400
Also,

44
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:29,110
your status as a special envoy
has been revoked.

45
00:03:29,110 --> 00:03:30,110
This token...

46
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,600
I brought it over.

47
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,970
Keep it as a memento.

48
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,960
Xiao Chi!

49
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,630
General Xiao.

50
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,470
Lord Xiao!

51
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,120
For the sake of the Grand Consort,

52
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,650
please let me off this time.

53
00:03:46,690 --> 00:03:47,210
Well,

54
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,120
I'll give you a way out.

55
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,720
As long as you tell me

56
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:53,180
why this girl beside me

57
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,800
came to find you,

58
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:57,210
I will plead with His Majesty for you.

59
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:59,430
Perhaps you can get a lighter sentence.

60
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:02,040
She said she was going to the capital

61
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,960
and wanted to use my special envoy token
to pass the checkpoint.

62
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,280
I said I would give it to her

63
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,480
as long as she could rescue me.

64
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,760
That's... that's all.

65
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,800
Zhao Gao,

66
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,310
do you know

67
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,050
if she is a spy from Changmo

68
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,750
and reaches the capital,

69
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:16,680
both the city and His Majesty
will be in grave danger.

70
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,390
I didn't collude with the enemy.

71
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,220
I... I didn't know she was a spy.

72
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,300
That's hard to say.

73
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:22,610
How about this?

74
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,720
I'll interrogate her myself

75
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,010
for Lord Zhao.

76
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:30,800
My Lord,

77
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,570
it's getting late.

78
00:04:32,570 --> 00:04:33,690
We can only rest at this inn

79
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:34,640
for the night

80
00:04:34,710 --> 00:04:37,070
and head to Tianlang Pass
early tomorrow morning.

81
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:37,800
That works.

82
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:40,360
You've all worked hard traveling
these past few days.

83
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,620
Let's get a good rest at this inn tonight.

84
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:43,420
Yes.

85
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,290
Where is the innkeeper?

86
00:04:56,890 --> 00:04:57,350
Huo Ran.

87
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:58,430
My Lord.

88
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,340
Go take a look.

89
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,270
Yes.

90
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:07,640
Drunkenly holding the golden goblet
to invite the moon to drink.

91
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:12,310
Half-parted lips asking
if my lover has arrived.

92
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:16,910
Where are you from?

93
00:05:17,150 --> 00:05:19,040
The most prosperous place of Jinglan—

94
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,770
the capital.

95
00:05:19,770 --> 00:05:21,060
The capital?

96
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,210
That's a nice place—

97
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,330
Moonlight flowing like water.

98
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,270
Lanterns bright as day.

99
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:31,390
Pity that I

100
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:34,120
have never been to such
a prosperous place.

101
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,230
May I ask

102
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,710
how should I address you?

103
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:44,360
You may call me

104
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:45,740
Fei Zheng.

105
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:47,700
A meeting is a matter of destiny.

106
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:48,870
Guest,

107
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,670
why don't you join me

108
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:51,820
for a drink?

109
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,310
Alright.

110
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,740
I happen to be thirsty.

111
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,240
Please.

112
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,520
You can really hold your liquor.

113
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,040
What's

114
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,310
your name?

115
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:11,490
My surname is Tang.

116
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:13,680
You can call me

117
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,000
Tang Zhaoxue.

118
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,800
Tang Zhaoxue.

119
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:21,380
To be an innkeeper here in Tianlang Pass,

120
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,070
you must know this place very well.

121
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,040
Of course.

122
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,190
I wonder

123
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:28,230
if I could ask you about someone.

124
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:29,120
Go ahead.

125
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,310
General Xiao,

126
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:32,770
Xiao Chi.

127
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,510
I wonder if you

128
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:36,290
have ever heard of him?

129
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,250
Him?

130
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:46,070
He's the man all the women in the city

131
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,920
dream of marrying.

132
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:53,620
General Xiao, is this okay?

133
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,130
Why wouldn't it be?

134
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,720
With your skills, General,

135
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,720
there's no need to lock the door

136
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,070
to interrogate a woman.

137
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:00,570
Just lock it when I tell you to.

138
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:02,500
If she is really a spy from Changmo,

139
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:05,120
we can't let her escape easily.

140
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:05,940
By the way,

141
00:07:06,180 --> 00:07:07,190
without my orders,

142
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,240
no one is allowed to come in.

143
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,000
Yes, sir.

144
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:12,560
This cell

145
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:15,150
used to be a place
for interrogating spies.

146
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:18,360
Though I've never used
these torture devices,

147
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,390
Miss Ling,

148
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,990
if you want to...

149
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:25,600
I wouldn't mind giving it a try.

150
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:28,430
I have been treating you.

151
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,260
So I guess I've done you a favor.

152
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:31,430
And I believe

153
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,390
you are an honorable man

154
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,010
and wouldn't torture me for a confession.

155
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:37,650
That's not it.

156
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:40,430
If you really are a spy from Changmo,

157
00:07:41,110 --> 00:07:42,350
then don't blame me

158
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,800
for repaying kindness with hostility.

159
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,600
It seems I can't hide it anymore.

160
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,480
Alright.

161
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,500
I will answer 3 of your questions.

162
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:51,700
I will answer truthfully

163
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:52,940
as long as you ask.

164
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:54,240
Why are you going to the capital?

165
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,000
To save someone.

166
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,510
Save who?

167
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,190
My brother.

168
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,620
Only one question is left.

169
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:01,350
Is she really the girl who saved me?

170
00:08:02,210 --> 00:08:03,240
Why can't I see a trace of the past

171
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,070
in her eyes?

172
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,070
Could she really be

173
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:10,130
the one I've missed for over 10 years?

174
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,180
But does she really not recognize me?

175
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,000
What is

176
00:08:15,180 --> 00:08:16,350
your real name?

177
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:21,720
Han Yunling.

178
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,700
Thank you, Physician Han.

179
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:25,750
I'm Physician Han Yunling.

180
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,720
I've answered 3 of your questions.

181
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,660
Could you answer 3 of mine?

182
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,260
What do you want to ask?

183
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,630
How can I leave the pass?

184
00:08:35,770 --> 00:08:37,289
It requires a border pass

185
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:38,510
written by me personally.

186
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:40,630
Then could you write a pass

187
00:08:40,669 --> 00:08:41,600
so I can leave?

188
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,510
No.

189
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,750
Why?

190
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:45,390
Our countries have been at war for years.

191
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:46,270
Changmo

192
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,650
constantly sends spies into Jinglan.

193
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,200
As the general guarding Tianlang Pass,

194
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,150
how could I possibly give

195
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,840
the written pass to a Changmo person

196
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,170
of unknown background?

197
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:58,220
If I were a bad person,
why would I save your life?

198
00:08:58,270 --> 00:08:59,810
You stayed at Tianlang Pass

199
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,170
just to figure out
how to go to the capital.

200
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:03,390
Am I right,

201
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,270
Miss Han Yunling?

202
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:10,750
If

203
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,510
you can tell me

204
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:14,200
your true identity

205
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,390
and purpose,

206
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,370
I might consider it.

207
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,270
I am just

208
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,460
an ordinary Changmo woman

209
00:09:21,460 --> 00:09:23,210
who knows a little medicine.

210
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:24,630
I'm not a spy.

211
00:09:24,650 --> 00:09:26,550
And I don't know any spies, either.

212
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:27,270
Okay.

213
00:09:28,370 --> 00:09:29,440
Then tomorrow,

214
00:09:29,810 --> 00:09:31,270
I will arrange for someone

215
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:33,470
to send you out of Tianlang Pass

216
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:34,870
and back to Changmo.

217
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:37,040
What about your illness then?

218
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:39,150
I'm the general of the border defense,

219
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:41,320
and you being from Changmo
with an unknown background—

220
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,510
to appease the troops,

221
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:45,370
I cannot accept
your long-term medical treatment.

222
00:09:49,690 --> 00:09:51,410
Since you have made up your mind,

223
00:09:51,410 --> 00:09:52,600
there's nothing I can do.

224
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,270
You're don't want to live.

225
00:09:54,570 --> 00:09:56,490
Don't blame my lack of medical skills.

226
00:09:56,490 --> 00:09:57,610
Of course not.

227
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,390
I've been frail since childhood.

228
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,630
Guarding Sirius Pass for years

229
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:02,200
has already taken a toll on my body.

230
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,440
Life and death—

231
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,730
I've long since made peace with it.

232
00:10:05,730 --> 00:10:06,760
But I...

233
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,960
All right.

234
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:15,200
I will leave Tianlang Pass tomorrow.

235
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:18,200
Let me treat you
one last time today.

236
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,030
Now?

237
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,030
Of course.

238
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,360
Right here?

239
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:25,270
This is the perfect place.

240
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,970
Please give me your hand.

241
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,090
What are you doing?

242
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:47,430
What on earth are you doing?

243
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,150
Please look.

244
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:53,310
The cold poison in your body
has built up in your spleen and kidneys.

245
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,480
Cold poison in the spleen

246
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,880
causes loss of appetite.

247
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,910
The kidneys are the foundation
of your constitution.

248
00:10:57,910 --> 00:11:00,030
When affected by cold poison,
it causes a pale face

249
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,150
and cold limbs.

250
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,080
After years of spreading,

251
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:05,030
it has accumulated from your arms

252
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:06,480
down to your hands.

253
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,150
So?

254
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:13,270
You don't have long left.

255
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:14,270
In that case,

256
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:16,160
I won't trouble you.

257
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:17,950
Release my pressure points.

258
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,550
Release it.

259
00:11:33,730 --> 00:11:36,060
I‘m going back
to Tianlang Pass tomorrow.

260
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:38,630
So, I'll give you a big gift today.

261
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:40,050
Is this a gift,

262
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,000
or revenge?

263
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,910
Who exactly is being interrogated?

264
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,970
Should I go over and take a look?

265
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:01,030
Forget it.

266
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:03,000
I'd better not disturb him.

267
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:05,670
Go back!

268
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:17,120
General Xiao, you can't even walk now?

269
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,790
You said you would escort me
out of Tianlang Pass tomorrow.

270
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:20,990
I always keep my word.

271
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:24,320
Alright, then go out by yourself.

272
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,150
Huang Jian.

273
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:47,360
Huang Jian!

274
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,870
Drink.

275
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,480
Come on.

276
00:13:00,310 --> 00:13:01,470
It's getting late.

277
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,890
I need to enter the pass tomorrow.

278
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:05,960
Miss, rest early.

279
00:13:09,130 --> 00:13:09,760
By the way.

280
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:16,720
Here is the money for the wine.

281
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,360
You're

282
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:31,320
very generous.

283
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,080
This gold

284
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:35,640
is enough to buy all the wine I have here.

285
00:13:35,730 --> 00:13:37,010
Then consider it

286
00:13:37,190 --> 00:13:38,590
that I've bought

287
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,700
out all your wine.

288
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,410
When the day comes,

289
00:13:41,410 --> 00:13:43,140
I'll have a good drink with you.

290
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,600
General,

291
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:57,860
are you feeling better?

292
00:13:57,860 --> 00:13:58,770
Much better.

293
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:02,000
You look much better than before.

294
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:04,850
It seems Dr. Ling is quite capable.

295
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,240
Why do you still want to send

296
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:08,220
her back to Changmo tomorrow?

297
00:14:09,340 --> 00:14:10,470
I've made up my mind.

298
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,730
Send her back to Changmo tomorrow morning.

299
00:14:13,730 --> 00:14:14,850
Report, General!

300
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,930
The patrol squad is fighting
with Changmo's men.

301
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,400
General Xiao.

302
00:14:21,090 --> 00:14:21,640
I'm fine.

303
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:24,810
Let's go to the city gate tower first.

304
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:28,190
General Xiao, I brought
the medicinal wine here.

305
00:14:30,410 --> 00:14:31,290
Physician Han.

306
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:33,170
Just leave it here for now.

307
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:38,600
Something happened at the city gate tower.

308
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,930
I need to go check it out.

309
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:41,670
Given your current condition,

310
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:43,670
you shouldn't move around too much.

311
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,750
If you insist on going,

312
00:14:45,770 --> 00:14:47,170
let me come with you

313
00:14:47,210 --> 00:14:48,690
in case of any emergency.

314
00:14:49,450 --> 00:14:51,110
How could that possibly work?

315
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,970
With your identity,

316
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,890
it's not appropriate
for you to enter the camp.

317
00:14:57,890 --> 00:14:58,600
I...

318
00:14:59,370 --> 00:15:01,980
What danger could a woman like me
possibly pose?

319
00:15:01,980 --> 00:15:03,980
Besides, your health is important.

320
00:15:04,580 --> 00:15:06,710
I don't want to see the treatment fail.

321
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,000
Report!

322
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:11,740
General, the Changmo army
used custom-made caltrops.

323
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:12,680
The wounded are in unbearable pain.

324
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,910
The medical camp sent me
to ask for your permission

325
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:15,060
to use opium for pain relief.

326
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,680
Go ahead. Why even ask about
such a small matter?

327
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:17,350
No.

328
00:15:18,090 --> 00:15:19,870
Opium is highly addictive if overused.

329
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:20,630
I have a way.

330
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:22,750
Right, Dr. Ling is from Changmo.

331
00:15:22,770 --> 00:15:24,170
She must have a solution.

332
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:26,510
General, I know about these caltrops.

333
00:15:26,850 --> 00:15:28,050
Besides, as a doctor,

334
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,590
I wouldn't refuse to save the wounded

335
00:15:29,590 --> 00:15:31,590
just because they are from Jinglan.

336
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,030
So many people are injured.

337
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,160
Apply the medicine!

338
00:15:47,970 --> 00:15:48,570
Let me see.

339
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:50,010
The Changmo people are treacherous.

340
00:15:50,010 --> 00:15:51,210
They injured our brothers.

341
00:15:51,210 --> 00:15:52,240
General, she...

342
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,940
Saving people is the priority now.

343
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:56,000
I would never gamble with your lives.

344
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:04,710
Bear with it.

345
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:13,390
Hold on.

346
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:15,950
Hold on.

347
00:16:16,220 --> 00:16:16,950
Bear with it.

348
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:18,950
Bear with it.

349
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,240
Hold on.

350
00:16:35,330 --> 00:16:36,090
That's it.

351
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:38,440
Thank you, Physician Han.

352
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:40,750
-Next one.
-Okay.

353
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:41,610
This way.

354
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:52,730
Physician Han.

355
00:16:55,030 --> 00:16:56,440
Thanks for your help this time.

356
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,440
It was no trouble.

357
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:01,190
You helped out this time.

358
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,670
Could it be...

359
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:07,280
A healer doesn't ask
about one's background.

360
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,720
I just want to do my best

361
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:10,410
to help more people.

362
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,700
But they are Jinglan people.

363
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,359
What if they're Jinglan people?

364
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:15,910
And what if they're Changmo people?

365
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:17,069
In my eyes,

366
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:20,109
there is only health and sickness.

367
00:17:21,470 --> 00:17:22,800
If everyone in the world

368
00:17:22,910 --> 00:17:24,220
were like you,

369
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,849
that would be great.

370
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:30,180
If only the world were at peace,

371
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:32,900
and everyone could live unharmed.

372
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:43,540
Will there ever be a day

373
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:44,940
when the world is at peace

374
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:47,590
and free from illness and disaster?

375
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:48,590
Of course it will.

376
00:17:57,130 --> 00:17:57,960
What's wrong?

377
00:17:58,060 --> 00:17:59,390
Are you feeling unwell?

378
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:01,440
No.

379
00:18:04,610 --> 00:18:07,070
I just remembered some things
from the past.

380
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:09,640
If you're fine,

381
00:18:09,650 --> 00:18:10,520
I'll be going.

382
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:11,980
Miss Han.

383
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:14,470
Thank you

384
00:18:16,190 --> 00:18:16,910
this time.

385
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:56,310
Go.

386
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,480
Good.

387
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:04,440
Good, good.

388
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,070
Everyone, count down from 3 with me.

389
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:09,960
3,

390
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:11,110
2,

391
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:12,720
1!

392
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:19,670
Any other folks want to give it a try?

393
00:19:19,690 --> 00:19:20,620
This young lady.

394
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:21,680
Come, miss.

395
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,610
That young lady.

396
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,440
Don't leave.

397
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,850
Yes, you. Come on.

398
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:29,070
-Miss, don't worry.
-What are you doing?

399
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:29,890
It's absolutely safe.

400
00:19:29,890 --> 00:19:30,920
-It's a family secret trick.
-Stop pulling me.

401
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,240
It's completely safe.

402
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:33,390
It's completely safe.

403
00:19:33,390 --> 00:19:33,710
I...

404
00:19:33,730 --> 00:19:34,650
It's completely safe.

405
00:19:34,650 --> 00:19:35,410
Don't worry.

406
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,050
Open the door.

407
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,030
Open the door!

408
00:19:40,810 --> 00:19:42,400
Folks,

409
00:19:42,430 --> 00:19:43,780
keep your eyes wide open,

410
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:45,300
hold your breath,

411
00:19:45,420 --> 00:19:47,020
and count down from 3 with me.

412
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:48,020
3.

413
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:49,830
2.

414
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:51,410
1!

415
00:19:55,290 --> 00:19:58,090
Good!

416
00:19:58,450 --> 00:19:59,450
That's amazing.

417
00:20:06,250 --> 00:20:08,010
Folks.

418
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:10,440
Anyone else want
to come up and give it a try?

419
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,110
If not,

420
00:20:12,130 --> 00:20:13,780
we'll wrap it up here.

421
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,440
What's going on?

422
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:17,800
Is she coming out or not?

423
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:20,290
Where is the girl from just now?

424
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:21,600
Which girl?

425
00:20:22,130 --> 00:20:23,750
The girl who just went in.

426
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:25,550
I didn't see her.

427
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:26,540
Open it.

428
00:20:27,380 --> 00:20:27,990
This...

429
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,920
Let's go.

430
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:38,540
They are running away.

431
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:41,020
Let me out!

432
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:42,350
Let me out!

433
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:44,450
Let me out now!

434
00:20:45,060 --> 00:20:46,610
Let me out!

435
00:21:06,370 --> 00:21:07,130
Stop!

436
00:21:16,630 --> 00:21:17,160
Yunling.

437
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:17,930
Yunling.

438
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:20,470
Yunling!

439
00:21:21,890 --> 00:21:22,400
Don't.

440
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:23,070
Don't.

441
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:23,790
Don't.

442
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:25,640
It's me.

443
00:21:25,870 --> 00:21:26,720
I'm Xiao Chi.

444
00:21:39,810 --> 00:21:40,830
I-It's alright now.

445
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:41,830
It's alright now.

446
00:21:46,500 --> 00:21:47,360
Physician Han.

447
00:21:47,810 --> 00:21:50,540
General asked me
to bring you this farewell wine.

448
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:51,300
He said

449
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:52,930
you were frightened today.

450
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:54,050
This is to help you settle your nerves

451
00:21:54,050 --> 00:21:55,050
and help you rest.

452
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:56,280
By the way,

453
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,510
General Xiao has military affairs
to handle,

454
00:21:58,510 --> 00:22:00,170
so he won't come to bother you.

455
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:04,350
General Xiao.

456
00:22:04,450 --> 00:22:06,580
Are you really sending Miss Ling back?

457
00:22:06,670 --> 00:22:09,000
Haven't you always suspected she's a spy?

458
00:22:09,180 --> 00:22:09,710
General.

459
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,060
Actually, I think she...

460
00:22:11,060 --> 00:22:11,920
That's enough.

461
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,570
Let's do it this way.

462
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:19,850
Miss Ling.

463
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:21,580
General Xiao said,

464
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:22,750
tomorrow...

465
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:26,160
tomorrow, he will personally
escort you out of the city.

466
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:43,030
Good!

467
00:22:43,610 --> 00:22:45,780
It seems you're recovering well.

468
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:49,340
Isn't it because
of your treatment, Physician Han?

469
00:22:50,420 --> 00:22:51,720
Just call me Han Yunling.

470
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,480
Then how should I thank you, Miss Han?

471
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,440
Getting better soon

472
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:56,960
would be the greatest thanks
you could give me.

473
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,550
I won't just recover quickly.

474
00:22:58,550 --> 00:23:00,270
I will also go to battle,

475
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:01,480
protect the people of Jinglan,

476
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,750
and protect you.

477
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,780
I don't know if you still remember me.

478
00:23:08,660 --> 00:23:10,790
But since I promised to protect you,

479
00:23:12,410 --> 00:23:13,060
then...

480
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,880
sending you away
from this place of trouble

481
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:18,960
is perhaps a kind of protection.

482
00:23:25,810 --> 00:23:26,870
Fine, I'll go back.

483
00:23:27,820 --> 00:23:29,950
I will definitely think of another way

484
00:23:29,980 --> 00:23:31,040
to save my brother.

485
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:39,800
General Xiao.

486
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,480
General Xiao.

487
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,280
General Xiao.

488
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:44,080
General Xiao.

489
00:23:44,250 --> 00:23:46,980
Are you really sending
Miss Ling back to Changmo?

490
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,240
Yes.

491
00:23:48,260 --> 00:23:49,710
Maybe you should reconsider.

492
00:23:49,710 --> 00:23:50,230
Lu Li.

493
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,330
In the past, no matter
what decision I made,

494
00:23:52,330 --> 00:23:54,190
you would obey unconditionally.

495
00:23:54,210 --> 00:23:55,210
What's wrong with you today?

496
00:23:55,210 --> 00:23:56,270
Well, it's just...

497
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:57,680
Enough. Say no more.

498
00:23:57,710 --> 00:23:58,710
My mind is made up.

499
00:24:00,490 --> 00:24:01,690
Where is Han Yunling?

500
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:02,590
I'll go look for her.

501
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:03,790
No need to look for me.

502
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,310
Don't you want to send me back?

503
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:12,680
Let's go.

504
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:14,580
Send me back to Changmo right now.

505
00:24:15,370 --> 00:24:16,500
What's wrong with you?

506
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:17,340
General Xiao,

507
00:24:17,380 --> 00:24:18,170
I suspect

508
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,980
it's because of the wine
you had me send her last night.

509
00:24:20,980 --> 00:24:22,700
That wasn't strong wine.

510
00:24:22,980 --> 00:24:23,700
It can't be.

511
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,230
Are we going or not?

512
00:24:27,330 --> 00:24:29,360
I'll grant your wish right now.

513
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:31,300
I can't stay here another second.

514
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,570
Fine.

515
00:24:33,340 --> 00:24:34,860
We'll settle this when I'm back.

516
00:24:34,860 --> 00:24:35,590
Keep an eye on her.

517
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:36,240
Let's go.

518
00:24:36,390 --> 00:24:37,820
In broad daylight,

519
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:39,230
General Xiao,
you have such refined tastes.

520
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:39,780
Don't stop me!

521
00:24:39,780 --> 00:24:40,300
Zheng?

522
00:24:40,320 --> 00:24:41,350
Physician Han, don't go over there.

523
00:24:41,350 --> 00:24:43,090
-What brings you here?
-I want to go out!

524
00:24:43,090 --> 00:24:44,610
His Majesty sent me to see

525
00:24:45,070 --> 00:24:46,630
-what exactly you've been up to
-Don't touch me.

526
00:24:46,630 --> 00:24:47,700
all these years at Tianlang Pass.

527
00:24:47,700 --> 00:24:48,600
You can't go there, Physician Han.

528
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,460
Physician Han.

529
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:50,270
Physician Han.

530
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:51,480
You've even learned
to force innocent women now?

531
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:52,280
Don't stop me.

532
00:24:52,290 --> 00:24:53,040
Let me take you back to your room.

533
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:54,610
Zheng, listen to me.

534
00:24:56,100 --> 00:24:57,170
No need to explain.

535
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:58,830
No, it's really nothing.

536
00:24:59,330 --> 00:24:59,830
Physician Han.

537
00:24:59,830 --> 00:25:00,650
Keep a close eye on her.

538
00:25:00,650 --> 00:25:01,490
Report!

539
00:25:03,550 --> 00:25:04,350
General Xiao,

540
00:25:04,390 --> 00:25:06,290
a Changmo general is challenging us
outside the pass.

541
00:25:06,290 --> 00:25:07,920
Seems I arrived just in time.

542
00:25:08,250 --> 00:25:09,240
There's a good show to watch.

543
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,300
Zheng, then please

544
00:25:10,530 --> 00:25:11,610
cheer for me.

545
00:25:11,860 --> 00:25:12,450
Alright.

546
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:16,440
Keep an eye on her.

547
00:25:16,510 --> 00:25:17,310
Wait for my return.

548
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:18,270
Yes.

549
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:21,960
[Shengde Gate]

550
00:25:23,570 --> 00:25:26,290
The marriage alliance is a major event.

551
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,960
We mustn't decide this in haste.

552
00:25:28,990 --> 00:25:31,030
Precisely because it's a major event,

553
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:33,750
Your Majesty should make a decision soon.

554
00:25:33,830 --> 00:25:37,350
I already sent Fei Zheng to Tianlang Pass

555
00:25:37,490 --> 00:25:40,300
to see what Changmo's intentions are.

556
00:25:40,330 --> 00:25:41,240
Your Majesty.

557
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:43,120
In my opinion,

558
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:46,180
Changmo just wants
to make peace with Jinglan.

559
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:48,850
They wouldn't dare
have any other intentions.

560
00:25:48,850 --> 00:25:50,350
Your Majesty worries too much.

561
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:51,350
Your Majesty.

562
00:25:51,410 --> 00:25:53,000
You are the Emperor.

563
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:55,090
Your personal affairs
are matters of state.

564
00:25:55,090 --> 00:25:57,090
You must not be careless.

565
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:58,830
You are still young.

566
00:25:59,390 --> 00:26:00,670
The three of us

567
00:26:00,950 --> 00:26:04,910
are the core ministers entrusted
to you by the late Emperor.

568
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:08,880
You must trust his judgment.

569
00:26:08,930 --> 00:26:10,260
Yes, Your Majesty.

570
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:16,050
The Eldest Princess has arrived.

571
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:29,240
Greetings, Eldest Princess.

572
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:44,570
I heard today's court discussion

573
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:47,510
is about the marriage alliance
between Jinglan and Changmo.

574
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:49,870
So I specially came to listen.

575
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:55,910
The marriage alliance document
from Changmo has been here for days.

576
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:59,960
We just hope His Majesty
makes a decision soon.

577
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:02,440
The marriage alliance
between Jinglan and Changmo

578
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:05,400
concerns the peace of both nations
and the lives of the people.

579
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:07,160
This cannot be taken lightly.

580
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:09,210
Even if my father were alive,

581
00:27:09,230 --> 00:27:11,510
he would consider it carefully.

582
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:13,400
His Majesty is not yet married.

583
00:27:13,420 --> 00:27:15,570
We does not have an empress yet.

584
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:18,310
If he takes a Princess of Changmo
into the palace first,

585
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:21,030
and she gives birth to a child,

586
00:27:21,030 --> 00:27:23,220
the royal bloodline may be compromised.

587
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:25,670
Do you all agree?

588
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:28,850
We believe every word Your Highness
said is reasonable.

589
00:27:28,870 --> 00:27:29,980
Of course.

590
00:27:30,010 --> 00:27:33,010
The Emperor's marriage is a major event.

591
00:27:33,030 --> 00:27:34,690
As for when the marriage will take place,

592
00:27:34,690 --> 00:27:36,610
we still have to listen to His Majesty.

593
00:27:36,610 --> 00:27:38,260
Once His Majesty decides,

594
00:27:38,370 --> 00:27:40,060
I will spare no expense.

595
00:27:40,080 --> 00:27:43,720
When the time comes, I will open
the treasury and allocate ample funds

596
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,680
to handle this matter properly.

597
00:27:46,290 --> 00:27:47,770
What

598
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,920
do the three of you think?

599
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:55,920
We will follow
the Eldest Princess's orders.

600
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:05,070
What does it say?

601
00:28:13,430 --> 00:28:15,760
If the princess sent for the alliance
is not well protected,

602
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:17,290
Jinglan will be destroyed?

603
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:20,810
His Majesty sent me

604
00:28:20,810 --> 00:28:22,330
for the marriage alliance

605
00:28:22,710 --> 00:28:24,990
to uncover Changmo's true intentions.

606
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,480
This way, we can be prepared.

607
00:28:27,830 --> 00:28:29,000
Rest assured, Zheng.

608
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:31,260
I will definitely defend Tianlang Pass.

609
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:34,120
With General Xiao here,

610
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,590
how can I not be at ease?

611
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:46,240
Take me out of the pass!

612
00:28:46,970 --> 00:28:48,230
How much did she drink?

613
00:28:48,350 --> 00:28:49,360
It's already this late,

614
00:28:49,360 --> 00:28:50,840
and she's still not sober.

615
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:53,020
Take me out of the pass!

616
00:28:57,450 --> 00:28:58,650
May I ask,

617
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:01,310
who exactly is this girl?

618
00:29:02,710 --> 00:29:04,310
My name is Han Yunling.

619
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:07,070
I am a physician from Changmo.

620
00:29:07,390 --> 00:29:08,950
I saved his life.

621
00:29:09,550 --> 00:29:11,150
But he won't listen to me

622
00:29:11,170 --> 00:29:12,900
and even wants to drive me away.

623
00:29:15,870 --> 00:29:17,800
I won't leave. I won't leave.

624
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:19,450
I will definitely cure you.

625
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:21,280
You also said
you would escort me to the capital.

626
00:29:21,280 --> 00:29:22,590
You promised me.

627
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:29,270
I...

628
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:30,590
This...

629
00:29:33,330 --> 00:29:34,580
Judging by your complexion,

630
00:29:34,580 --> 00:29:36,340
you look much better

631
00:29:36,570 --> 00:29:37,700
than when we parted.

632
00:29:38,570 --> 00:29:40,810
It seems she has some skills.

633
00:29:41,890 --> 00:29:44,120
What a pity that the imperial physician
His Majesty sent with me

634
00:29:44,120 --> 00:29:45,970
won't be needed.

635
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,290
She is skilled.

636
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:54,880
But she

637
00:29:56,130 --> 00:29:57,160
is from Changmo.

638
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:59,380
So what if she is from Changmo?

639
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:01,360
Our countries
have been at war for years,

640
00:30:01,360 --> 00:30:02,030
and I

641
00:30:02,340 --> 00:30:03,540
guard Tianlang Pass.

642
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,270
So that's

643
00:30:05,550 --> 00:30:07,480
why you're sending her away today?

644
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:12,010
You're afraid she'll poison you

645
00:30:12,010 --> 00:30:12,930
and harm you?

646
00:30:13,500 --> 00:30:14,300
She won't.

647
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:16,290
Then what are you afraid of?

648
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,450
Not everyone in Changmo is bad.

649
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:21,900
Since she can cure your chronic illness,

650
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,200
why not keep her here?

651
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:27,550
Looking at it this way,

652
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,400
you two are quite a match.

653
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:31,030
Zheng,

654
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:33,030
what are you talking about?

655
00:30:33,030 --> 00:30:35,110
I'm saying exactly what I mean.

656
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:36,360
It's settled then.

657
00:30:36,490 --> 00:30:37,770
Keep her here

658
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:39,260
to continue treating you.

659
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:40,770
It won't be considered colluding
with the enemy.

660
00:30:40,770 --> 00:30:41,770
You have my word.

661
00:30:42,350 --> 00:30:43,240
How could that possibly work?

662
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,350
Why not?

663
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:45,110
Tomorrow,

664
00:30:45,560 --> 00:30:48,170
I'll have the imperial physician,
who hasn't left the palace in a long time,

665
00:30:48,170 --> 00:30:49,650
watch her treat you.

666
00:30:49,820 --> 00:30:51,620
Let him learn something from it.

667
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:53,880
Zheng.

668
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:54,580
I...

669
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,960
I haven't seen Chu in a long time.

670
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,680
I wonder how he's doing.

671
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,640
His Majesty.

672
00:31:04,190 --> 00:31:04,880
He...

673
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,530
is doing well.
